VERIFICATION
============

Verification is intended to assist the Chocolatey moderators and end users
in verifying that this package's contents are trustworthy.

Package version: {{VERSION}}

The MSI installers downloaded by this package are produced and signed by the
official NSClient++ build pipeline at
<https://github.com/mickem/nscp/actions> and published as release assets at
<https://github.com/mickem/nscp/releases/tag/{{RELEASE_TAG}}>.

To verify the binaries:

1. Download the installers directly from the release page:
     {{URL_MSI_X64}}
     {{URL_MSI_X86}}

2. Compute their SHA256 checksums:
     Get-FileHash -Algorithm SHA256 NSCP-{{VERSION}}-x64.msi
     Get-FileHash -Algorithm SHA256 NSCP-{{VERSION}}-Win32.msi

3. The expected hashes are:
     x64    : {{SHA256_MSI_X64}}
     x86    : {{SHA256_MSI_X86}}

4. Optionally inspect the Authenticode signature, which is issued via Azure
   Trusted Signing to "MySolutions NORDIC".

